text: Desmiphora dozieri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2007. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora dozieri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 2007
